     <h2>How to play</h2>
     <p><b>Goal:</b> destroy the enemy Town Center in the far corner of the map before they destroy yours.</p>
     <p><b>Select:</b> left-click a unit, or drag a box around several. <b>Order:</b> right-click to move, gather (on trees, berries, gold), or attack an enemy.</p>
